column4: b'Give the gift of homemade this Christmas. This holiday favorite makes up to one gallon of easy, delicious sweet pickles or pickled peppers to share with friends and family this holiday season. No cooking or canning required! Start with a jar of dill pickle slices or yellow pepper rings and follow the simple directions to complete with just a few basic kitchen ingredients. You will be amazed with the results and the raves you will receive. Packet includes the story "Legend of the Christmas Pickle." Start your own family tradition today!'
